snippet.textDisplay:
Can a knowledgeable person imagine that he can, all by himself, identify the chronic illnesses of the world and come to know the variety of diseases that afflict contingent existence; that he can diagnose the maladies of the people of the earth or the painful condition of human society; or that he can uncover the hidden mysteries of ages and centuries? Could he discover the necessary relationships that derive from the realities of things, or legislate an order and laws that would constitute a quick cure or a complete remedy? There is not the slightest doubt that it is impossible. Thus, it is evident and has been established that the one who legislates ordinances, order, canon law and civil laws among humankind is God, the Mighty, the All-Knowing. For no one but the incomparable Lord is aware and informed of the realities of existence, the abstrusities of every being, the hidden mystery, and the recondite enigmas of eras and ages. For this reason, European law is still imperfect and incomplete, still in the realm of change and alteration or repeal and amendment even though it is in reality the result of several thousand years of thinking by constitutional scholars and political philosophers. For the learned of the past had not discovered the harmfulness of some laws, whereas later scholars became aware of it. Therefore, some laws are amended, some are reaffirmed, and some are altered.

Indeed, let us go to the heart of the matter. The revealed law is like the spirit of life, and civil government is like the power of salvation. The revealed law is like the shining sun, and the civil government is like April clouds. These two radiant stars are like two points in a constellation above the horizon of the contingent world that shine down on the people of the world.
'Abdu'l-Bahá's "Treatise on Leadership"
(Risalih-'i Siyasiyyih):
Trans. Juan R. I. Cole

snippet.textDisplay: Also, 2 months ago (after my flight back to the US and quarantine,) I remembered that when I was in Wuhan I saw this -> "lockdown" measure taken and experienced it. - I also saw this type measures by police targeting different Province car tags redirecting them... I believe it can be done. But it needs to be well thought out and strategically planned.  When I landed into California from Wuhan on the first flight, I noticed that FEMA had a proper quarantine set-up only after the first week.. The CDC were ready. I remember working with FEMA years ago designing Modular Command Center Vehicles through another company and I saw that Emergency Law Enforcement and Medical Command were much better prepared then than now. I AM very surprised.. But the CDC was doing their best making sure the Medical was set up.. So seeing the US not so prepared starting back when the virus was first seen in cases in the US from China, was very surprising to me.. I saw what happened in Wuhan and lived through that!.. So why was the US not getting things prepared on DAY 1 ??   Not to mention the flights were called "Evacuation Flights". - WE are paying $1000 for the flight! - So it cannot be n evacuation flight..  Such a shame.. We should have stayed prepared
